    <tr>
      <td>LSTM</td>
      <td>0.667</td>
      <td>0.635</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>DistilBERT Fine Tuned</td>
      <td><strong>0.685</strong></td>
      <td><strong>0.674</strong></td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>Table 1: Overall accuracy of the two models</p>

